<h1>In focus</h1>

<%= link_to 'Change focus', change_focus_path %>

<p>You’re focussing on the following unknowns. Each week you’ll receive a reminder to quickly reflect on your progress towards becoming more confident in them. Your next reminder is on <strong><%= next_reminder_date.strftime("%a %e %b") %></strong>, but you can add insights any time.</p>

<table>
  <thead>
    <tr>
      <th>Title</th>
      <th>Author</th>
      <th></th>
    </tr>
  </thead>

  <tbody>
    <% @foci.each do |unknown| %>
      <tr>
        <td><%= unknown.title %></td>
        <td><%= unknown.author.username %></td>
        <td><%= link_to 'Show', unknown %></td>
      </tr>
    <% end %>
  </tbody>
</table>
